<lb n="0402a06" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0402a0601">鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>娑囉莎帝<note place="inline">引</note>輸<note place="inline">引</note>達野吽<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0402a07" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0402a0701">鉢訥謨<note place="inline">二合引</note>哩馱<note place="inline">二合</note>昂<note place="inline">引</note>嚩尸酤嚕<g ref="#CB00763">𠺁</g><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0402a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0402a0801">如是等蓮華部印智。</p>
<lb n="0402a09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="018" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說一切如來真實攝大乘現證三昧大教王
<lb n="0402a10" ed="T"/>經卷第十八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body>
